亂黎<br />\n<br />\n所以個重點就係點樣利用人多呢個優點阿"},{"pid":"65da7132d5036153e83afe51f988d34e30be2505","tid":1504630,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:58:24.000Z","msg":"推阿"},{"pid":"3fc507b9ebfd191bdb4015918c03585a8923fc1a","tid":1504630,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282025acf3da69c5e8a15078363425f1a1013171","tid":1504630,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉打經濟牌 求下大家"},{"pid":"cbadab832b5a0e7973917ffba269648aaf7e9e24","tid":1504630,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2757de0e0262d6da0af6edd21db7e0936fd5d98e","tid":1504630,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc2bfa8ef759dc54890f10a50ba14f8d0b14cec","tid":1504630,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"係機場狗狗用唔到tg/水炮車<br />\n一旦肉搏我方必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74127646d807f14ab921675ed8e30dd219e50028","tid":1504630,"uid":31020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc2bfa8ef759dc54890f10a50ba14f8d0b14cec","tid":1504630,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"係機場狗狗用唔到tg/水炮車<br />\n一旦肉搏我方必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201